## Install

[%- if .CIGitHub %]

```bash
curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/[% .GitUser %]/[% .ProjectName %]/main/install.sh | sh
```

[%- end %]

**Go install**:

```bash
go install [% .ModulePath %]@latest
```

**From source**:

```bash
git clone [% .RepoURL %].git
cd [% .ProjectName %]
make build    # Binary at bin/[% .BinaryName %]
```

## Usage

```bash
[% .BinaryName %] --help
```

## Development

```bash
make build          # Build binary
make test           # Run tests
make lint           # Run linters
make format         # Format code
```

## Shell Completion

```bash
# Bash
source <([% .BinaryName %] completion bash)

# Zsh
source <([% .BinaryName %] completion zsh)

# Fish
[% .BinaryName %] completion fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/[% .BinaryName %].fish
```
